# EduNet College Portal – Implementation Plan

LAN-only offline lab portal. Subject → Assignment workflow. Verified against actual codebase.

> [!NOTE]
> **Confirmed from code:** HTTP server = `:8080`, TCP = `:7878`, UDP = `:5000`, broadcast every 30s. No MongoDB exists yet.

---

## Architecture

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Browser --> H["Actix :8080\nmain.rs"]
    H --> Lab["lab_module\n(new)"]
    Lab --> Mongo["MongoDB :27017\nneuromesh_lab"]
    Lab --> Store["/lab_storage/"]
    UDP["UDP :5000\nudp/mod.rs"] -- "LAB_ASSIGNMENT\n(extend BroadcastMessage)" --> Students
    TCP["TCP :7878\ntcp/mod.rs"] -- "FILE: marker (reuse)" --> FileUpload
```

