## Phase 3 · Rust Backend (`src/lab_module/`)

```toml
# Cargo.toml — add:
mongodb = { version = "2", features = ["tokio-runtime"] }
```

```
src/lab_module/
 ├── mod.rs              # pub fn config(cfg) — registers all /api/ routes
 ├── mongo_connection.rs # Lazy<Client> singleton  
 ├── role_auth.rs        # POST /api/auth/login
 ├── subject_manager.rs  # GET /api/subjects/teacher/{id}, /api/subjects/student/{id}
 ├── assignment_manager.rs # POST /create /start/{id} /close/{id}, GET /active
 ├── submission_manager.rs # GET /api/assignments/{id}/submissions + /export (CSV)
 ├── file_transfer.rs    # POST /api/upload — validates, saves to /lab_storage/, inserts submission doc
 └── scheduler.rs        # tokio::spawn loop every 30s — sets is_active=false past deadline
```

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Wire into existing [main.rs](file:///e:/Hackathon/AISSMS/src/main.rs) by adding `mod lab_module;` and `.service(web::scope("/api").service(llm::chat).configure(lab_module::config))`.

