## Phase 4 · UDP Broadcast Extension

Extend existing [udp/mod.rs](file:///e:/Hackathon/AISSMS/src/udp/mod.rs) [BroadcastMessage](file:///e:/Hackathon/AISSMS/src/udp/mod.rs#30-35) struct — add optional `lab_assignment` field:

```rust
// Extend existing BroadcastMessage:
struct BroadcastMessage {
    message_type: String,    // existing
    has_llm: bool,           // existing
    timestamp: DateTime<Utc>,// existing
    lab_assignment: Option<LabAssignmentBroadcast>, // NEW
}
```

When `assignment.is_active == true`, populate `lab_assignment` in every 30s broadcast.

